    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The rain falls in sheets, soaking through your threadbare cloak. Behind you, the cottage burns\u2014your safe haven of eight years, reduced to smoking timber. Flames reflect in the puddles, orange and violent against the grey dawn.\n\nYou don't look back. Looking back is how they catch you.\n\nYour satchel holds everything: three books of void magic written in your mother's hand, a locket with her portrait, and a map of Crownhaven you memorized years ago.\n\nThe crown piece waits in the catacombs beneath the old imperial palace. Your parents died protecting that secret.",
