    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Ashen Marches stretch before you\u2014a wasteland where the old world died. The ground crunches with ash, and the air tastes of sulfur and regret.\n\nYou see them in the distance: half-formed things, twisted creatures that emerged from the Sundering. They watch you with eyes that hold no light.\n\nThe Watch guards the border\u2014mercenary knights paid to kill what crawls from the Waste. They could help you. Or they could take everything.\n\nA child cries somewhere in the darkness. Abandoned. Alone.\n\nThe void pulses in your veins, demanding to be used.",
