  "KIRA_CH1_CIRCLE": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_CIRCLE",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Circle of Mages hides in plain sight\u2014a tower that appears different to each observer. You climb the stairs, each step taking you further from the world you knew.\n\nThe Archmage awaits at the top. An ageless woman with silver hair and eyes that see through time.\n\n'We know who you are, Kira Nightwind,' she says. 'We felt your void magic from across the kingdom.'\n\nShe knows about the crown. About your parents. About the Cult.\n\n'We can help you,' she offers. 'But the price is your service.'",
