  "KIRA_CH1_BANDITS": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_BANDITS",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "Three bandits. One merchant wagon. A family pleading for their lives.\n\nThe void surges within you\u2014a tide of darkness that wants to be released. You've hidden for eight years. Fed on scraps. Pretended to be nothing.\n\nNo more.\n\nYour fingers blur with shadows. The first bandit falls before he understands what's happening. The second turns to run, but shadows wrap around his throat.\n\nThe third kneels, trembling. 'Mercy,' he whimpers. 'We're with the Cult\u2014we were just\u2014'\n\nThe Cult. They're already here.",
