  "KIRA_CH1_CHILD": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_CHILD",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The child is a boy, no more than six. Hollow eyes stare from a face too thin, too old for his years.\n\n'Don't hurt me,' he whispers. 'Please.'\n\nYou reach out with the void\u2014not to harm, but to shield. Shadows wrap around him like a blanket, warm and safe. The creatures of the Waste recoil from the darkness.\n\nWhen you remove your hands, something has changed. The boy looks at you with wonder, not fear.\n\n'You're like me,' he says. 'The shadows listen to you.'\n\nAnd then you feel it: the void within him, small but real. He's one of you.",
