  "KIRA_CH1_WATCH": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_WATCH",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Watch is everything the kingdoms pretend not to know\u2014a wall of steel and sacrifice against the dying world.\n\nTheir commander is a scarred woman named Voss. She looks at you with knowing eyes.\n\n'A Nightwind,' she says. 'We wondered when you'd show.'\n\nShe knows your family. Your legacy. The burden you carry.\n\n'The Cult is moving,' she continues. 'All seven pieces of Aethon's crown. They're going to reunite them at the Temple of the Void. And when they do...'\n\nShe doesn't finish. She doesn't have to.",
