  "KIRA_CH1_WASTELAND": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_WASTELAND",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "You walk through the wasteland for three days. The ash never stops falling. The sky is permanently grey, as if the sun itself died with the Void Kingdom.\n\nOn the second night, you find the skeleton of a giant\u2014something from the old world. Its bones are black as coal, and when you touch them, you feel the void pulse.\n\nThere's power here. Ancient, terrible power.\n\nAnd something else: a piece of the crown, embedded in the skeleton's chest. It calls to you like a voice from a nightmare.\n\nThe first piece. Just... sitting there. Waiting.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
