  "KIRA_CH1_OFFER": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_OFFER",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Archmage's offer is simple: serve the Circle for five years, and they will help you destroy the Cult.\n\nBut you see the truth in her eyes. They don't want to destroy the crown\u2014they want to control it.\n\n'Your parents made the same choice,' she says. 'They served us, then betrayed us. Look where it got them.'\n\nYour parents served the Circle? The thought makes your stomach turn.\n\n'Accept our help,' she presses, 'or walk away. But know this: the Cult already knows you're alive. They know where you're going. And they have more mages than you can imagine.'",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Accept the offer",
