  "KIRA_CH1_TRUTH": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_TRUTH",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Archmage tells you everything.\n\nThe crown was Aethon's power\u2014seven pieces, each containing a fragment of the first silence. When united, they could unmake reality itself.\n\nYour parents were guardians\u2014chosen to protect the pieces. When the Cult came for them, they hid one piece in you. Literally, within your soul.\n\n'That's why they can find you,' the Archmage says. 'The piece calls to its brothers. And the Cult hears its voice.'\n\nYou have a piece of the crown inside you. And it's been calling the Cult since the day you were born.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Let the Circle remove it",
