  "KIRA_CH1_INTERROGATE": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_INTERROGATE",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "You keep one bandit alive\u2014make him talk.\n\nThe Cult has been hunting Nightwinds for generations. Your family was the last. They killed your parents eight years ago, but missed you.\n\n'Vespera will want to know you're alive,' the bandit gasps. 'She'll send the Hollow Knights. The seven pieces must be united at the Temple\u2014'\n\nHe dies before saying more. But you know now: Vespera. The Temple. The seven pieces.\n\nThis is bigger than revenge. This is the end of the world.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
