  "KIRA_CH1_AFTERMATH": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_AFTERMATH",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The merchant is grateful. He offers you a ride to Crownhaven, and something more: information.\n\n'I know about the Cult,' he whispers. 'I used to trade with them\u2014until I saw what they do to children. They want to reunite the crown\u2014bring back the Void Kingdom. But there's something worse waiting to be freed.'\n\nHe gives you a symbol\u2014a silver crescent. 'The Circle of Mages. Find them. They'll help you, even if the world won't.'\n\nYou take the road to Crownhaven, the symbol heavy in your pocket, the void heavy in your soul.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
