  "KIRA_CH1_ORPHAN": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_ORPHAN",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Circle accepts the boy. They see the void in him\u2014another potential weapon against the Cult.\n\nBut they want you to train him. To pass on what you know. To become a teacher when you wanted only to survive.\n\n'He has talent,' the Archmage says. 'But so did your parents. And we all know how that ended.'\n\nYou train the boy for three months. His name is Tom. He's afraid of the dark but fascinated by it. Just like you once were.\n\nWhen you finally leave for Crownhaven, he cries. And you realize: you've started a chain that might outlast you.",
    "choices": [
