  "KIRA_CH1_PARENTS": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH1_PARENTS",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "Commander Voss tells you what she knows.\n\nYour parents were Kira and Marcus Nightwind\u2014two of the most powerful void mages of their generation. They protected crown pieces for forty years.\n\n'The Cult finally caught them in your village,' Voss says. 'Your mother fought. Your father died protecting you. Your mother...'\n\nShe pauses.\n\n'Your mother made a deal. She gave herself to the Hollow King in exchange for your life. That's why you still live. That's why the Cult keeps hunting you\u2014because you're the key to bringing her back.'\n\nYour mother isn't dead. She's worse than dead. She's a prisoner of a god.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Swear to free her",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_CH2_CROWNHAVEN",
        "effects": {
          "void_magic": 1
        },
        "requires": null
