        "effects": {
          "stealth": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "KIRA_CH2_BATTLE": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH2_BATTLE",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Hollow Knight is faster than any human. Its sword moves like thought\u2014strike, parry, counter.\n\nBut you're faster.\n\nThe void answers your call. Shadows tear from the walls, wrapping around the Knight's limbs. You pour everything into the magic\u2014eight years of hiding, eight years of fear, eight years of rage.\n\nThe Knight screams\u2014a sound like tearing metal\u2014and dissolves into darkness.\n\nYou stand alone in the chamber, breathing hard. The crown piece pulses with\u6b22\u8fce.\n\nYour mother left you a message, etched in void light: 'Forgive me. Find the truth. And when you're ready\u2014destroy it all.'",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Take the crown piece",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_CH2_CROWN",
        "effects": {
          "void_magic": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Read your mother's message first",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_CH2_MESSAGE",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Destroy the piece\u2014end the cycle",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_CH2_DESTROY",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": -2
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "KIRA_CH2_NEGOTIATE": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH2_NEGOTIATE",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "'The Master wants you alive,' the Hollow Knight says. 'The others... less so.'\n\nYou keep your voice steady. 'Who is your Master? What does he want?'\n\n'The Hollow King. He wants the crown. And he wants you\u2014specifically. Your bloodline created the seal. Your bloodline can break it.'\n\nThe Hollow Knight steps aside. Not defeated\u2014allowing.\n\n'Take the piece, Kira Nightwind. Bring it to the Temple. And meet your mother.'\n\nSomething cold settles in your stomach. Your mother is alive. But at what cost?",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Take the crown piece",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_CH2_CROWN",
        "effects": {
