  "KIRA_CH2_BYPASS": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH2_BYPASS",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "You become shadow\u2014pure, formless darkness. The Knight passes through you, sensing nothing.\n\nIn the chamber, you see the crown piece without obstacles. It's smaller than you imagined\u2014a ring of black metal that seems to absorb light.\n\nYou reach for it\u2014and visions explode through your mind.\n\nAethon the Undying, screaming as the Void Beast tears his soul apart. His last act\u2014shattering the crown, sending the pieces across time. Seven fragments, seven guardians, seven sacrifices.\n\nAnd then you see her: your mother, trapped in a cage of void light, screaming your name.\n\nThe vision releases you. The crown piece is in your hand. And the Hollow Knight is turning.",
    "choices": [
