  "KIRA_CH2_CROWN": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH2_CROWN",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The crown piece is warm in your hand. Almost alive. It whispers secrets of the void\u2014the language of nothing itself.\n\nYou feel the other pieces, scattered across the kingdoms. Six more fragments, each calling to this one. The Cult has five. The Circle has one. And now you hold the seventh.\n\nIn your mind, you see the map: the Temple of the Void, deep in the Ashen Wastes. The final convergence. The reunification.\n\nYour mother will be there. The Hollow King will be there. And the fate of the world will be decided.\n\nThree paths forward. Which will you take?",
    "choices": [
