  "KIRA_CH2_ESCAPE": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH2_ESCAPE",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "You run through the catacombs, the crown piece burning in your pocket. Behind you, the Hollow Knight's screams echo off the stone.\n\nYou emerge into the night air, gasping. Crownhaven spreads before you\u2014a million lights, a million lives, none knowing what's coming.\n\nThe piece pulses: six more fragments, drawing closer. The Cult knows you have this one. They'll send everything.\n\nIn your mind, you see your mother's face\u2014not as she is now, trapped in the void, but as she was: laughing, teaching you magic, holding you when you were afraid.\n\nYou won't let her down.",
    "choices": [
