  "KIRA_CH3_TEMPLE": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH3_TEMPLE",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "The Temple of the Void stands at the heart of the Ashen Wastes\u2014a tower of black stone that hurts to look at. Reality bends around it, as if the world itself doesn't want to exist here.\n\nSix Cultists stand around a dais. Each holds a crown piece. Each wears a mask of silver.\n\nAnd in the center, suspended in a cage of pure void light: your mother.\n\n'Kira.' Her voice is barely a whisper. 'You shouldn't have come.'\n\nThe seventh piece in your hand begins to glow. The six in the Cultists' possession flare in response.\n\nThe Hollow King is here. And he's been waiting for you.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Charge\u2014save your mother",
