  "KIRA_CH3_CHARGE": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH3_CHARGE",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "You throw yourself at the Cultists, the void blazing from your hands. They fall\u2014shadows torn apart by shadows.\n\nBut there are more. Always more.\n\nThe Hollow King manifests: a formless thing of darkness and hunger. It wraps around you, squeezing the air from your lungs.\n\n'Your bloodline made me,' it hisses. 'Your great-great-grandfather bound me here. Now you'll undo it.'\n\nYour mother screams. The crown pieces fly toward you\u2014seven fragments becoming one.\n\nAnd you understand: this is the choice. Become the Undying, or die trying.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Claim the crown\u2014become a god",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_ENDING_UNDYING",
        "effects": {
          "void_magic": 5
