        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "KIRA_CH3_TALK": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH3_TALK",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "You reach through the void connection, finding your mother's mind.\n\nShe's been here for eight years\u2014trapped, tortured, turned slowly to shadow. But she's still fighting.\n\n'The crown is a trap,' she whispers. 'Aethon didn't seal the Beast\u2014he became it. The crown is its prison, and whoever wears it becomes the jailer.'\n\nThe Hollow King screams as he feels your intrusion. Your mother's last act of will tears a hole in his concentration.\n\n'Now,' she gasps. 'While he's weak\u2014finish it.'\n\nThe seven pieces fly toward you. But which choice will you make?",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Destroy the crown\u2014and yourself with it",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_ENDING_MARTYR",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": -3
