  "KIRA_CH3_BARGAIN": {
    "id": "KIRA_CH3_BARGAIN",
    "character": "KIRA",
    "description": "'Take me,' you say. 'Let her go. I'm the last Nightwind. I'm what you want.'\n\nThe Hollow King pauses. Your mother screams\u2014no, no, no\u2014\n\n'Kira, don't\u2014'\n\n'Very well.' The darkness wraps around you. It feels like drowning in ice. 'Your mother will live. But you'll spend eternity in the void with me.'\n\nYour mother falls free as you're pulled into the darkness. The last thing you see is her face\u2014tears streaming, reaching for you.\n\nAnd then there's only the void. And the hunger.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Embrace the darkness",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_ENDING_HOLLOW",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": -5
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Fight from within",
        "leads_to": "KIRA_ENDING_UNDYING",
