  "THERON_CH1_LEAVE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_LEAVE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You stand abruptly, the chair scraping against the floor. 'Find someone else. I don't do politics. I don't do redemption. I don't do queens.'\n\nMorgana's voice follows you to the door. 'The princess knew your name, Theron. She screamed it. And you left her to burn.'\n\nYou pause at the threshold. The void roars inside you, demanding silence.\n\n'You're already dead,' she calls. 'A man walking around in a corpse. That's not living\u2014that's hiding. And we both know it.'\n\nYou walk into the night. The cold air hits your face, and for a moment, you feel nothing at all.\n\nBut three blocks later, you're stealing a sword from a drunk guard. And heading toward Thornwick.\n\nMaybe death is better than this emptiness. Maybe this mission is just a complicated way to end it.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Go to Thornwick\u2014find the Cult",
