  "THERON_CH1_DELAY": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_DELAY",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "One more day. That's all you ask. One more day to drink, to pretend, to ignore the call of the void.\n\nBut the void doesn't wait. It never waits.\n\nThat night, you dream of flames. Princess Elara stands in the center of a burning room, her hands raised, calling for you. You reach for her\u2014and your hands pass through like smoke.\n\nShe burns. And you watch.\n\nDawn brings sickness, not answers. Your hands shake. Your head pounds. And worst of all: the dream won't fade.\n\nYou find Morgana's address. But something has changed. You're not doing this for redemption anymore. You're doing it because if you stop, you'll drown in the flames.",
