  "THERON_CH1_CONFRONT": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_CONFRONT",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You turn back, your hand on the door. 'Your ring. The crescent moon and shadow.'\n\nMorgana freezes. For a moment, something flashes in her eyes\u2014fear?\n\n'The old priesthood,' you continue. 'They served the Void before the kingdom was born. And that symbol\u2014it matches the Cult's marks.'\n\nShe slowly turns, her hand going to the ring. 'There are two kinds of people in this world, Theron. Those who serve the void, and those who use it against itself.'\n\nShe removes the ring, placing it on the table. 'I was young when they took me. A priestess of the old ways. But I found the light instead\u2014the queen's light. And I've spent thirty years fighting what I was.'\n\nHer eyes meet yours. 'Now do you understand? They want me dead. They've tried before. I need someone who knows their darkness.'",
    "choices": [
