  "THERON_CH1_JOURNEY": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_JOURNEY",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The road to Thornwick winds through the Ashen Hills\u2014a territory that hasn't recovered from the old wars. Burnt trees dot the landscape like skeletal fingers reaching for a sky that never lightens.\n\nYou travel for three days. The void keeps you company\u2014it whispers of danger ahead, of traps and treachery. You stopped questioning it years ago.\n\nOn the second night, you make camp near an abandoned village. The houses are blackened, their occupants long since fled or taken. The Cult did this, you know. Their work.\n\nYou find a survivor hiding in a cellar\u2014an old woman, half-mad with fear.\n\n'They took the children,' she whispers. 'All of them. For the Convergence. The shadow lady will be so pleased.'\n\nThe shadow lady. Vespera.\n\nShe dies in your arms before you can learn more. But the word stays with you: Convergence. Something big is coming.",
    "choices": [
