  "THERON_CH1_ALLIES": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_ALLIES",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You don't go to Thornwick alone. Old contacts remain\u2014mercenaries, spies, other broken knights who owe you favors from a life you try to forget.\n\nThere's Garreth, a former guard captain who lost his commission for drinking. Brynn, a thief who once tried to pick your pocket and ended up owing you her life. Old Marcus, a healer with no love for the queen but deep hatred for the Cult.\n\nThey gather in a seedy tavern in the lower city, their faces carved by years of survival. They look at you with something like hope.\n\n'The Ashfield Cult,' you tell them. 'We've heard stories. Bad ones.' Brynn shakes her head. 'They take children, Theron. For rituals. For sacrifices.'\n\nGarreth spits on the floor. 'The queen's court is compromised. Everyone knows it. But no one can prove it.'\n\nYou have your team. Now you need a plan.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
