  "THERON_CH1_RESEARCH": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_RESEARCH",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You spend two days in the great library of Thornwick\u2014or what's left of it. The Cult burned most of the records, but some survived.\n\nThe Ashfield Cult emerged thirty years ago, following the old king's death. They worship the Void\u2014that primordial darkness before creation. Their goal: the Convergence, when all shadows merge into one, ending the world as we know it.\n\nTheir leader, Vespera, was once a priestess of the Light. She was beautiful once\u2014a saint, they called her. But something broke her. Or perhaps she was always broken, waiting to be unleashed.\n\nThe records mention artifacts: seven shards of the Void Crown, scattered after the Sundering. The Cult has six. The seventh is hidden.\n\nAnd when they reunite all seven shards... the Convergence will begin.\n\nYou close the last book. The world is stranger than you knew. And darker.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Find the seventh shard\u2014stop the Convergence",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_SHARD",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Confront Vespera directly\u2014end this now",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH1_JOURNEY",
        "effects": {
          "strength": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
