    ]
  },
  "THERON_CH1_AMBUSH": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_AMBUSH",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The road through the hills narrows into a canyon. Bad territory. You should know better\u2014once, you were a knight who understood tactics.\n\nBut the void doesn't warn you. It wants this.\n\nArrows strike from the rocks above. You twist, one piercing your shoulder, but the others miss. You draw your stolen sword and charge the shadows.\n\nCultists drop from the rocks\u2014six of them, blades gleaming with poison. Their eyes are empty, their faces flat. They've given themselves to the void. There's no reasoning with them.\n\nYou fight with forgotten skill\u2014the training of a lifetime muscle memory. The void responds, lending you strength you thought was gone. The first two fall. Then the third. But more keep coming.\n\nAn arrow takes you in the leg. You go down. And the Cultists circle, ready to finish it.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Fight to the death\u2014don't give up",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH1_SURVIVE",
        "effects": {
