  "THERON_CH1_SURVIVORS": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_SURVIVORS",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You search the ruins for two days. Most are dead\u2014but a few survived, hiding in basements and crawlspaces.\n\nA young boy, perhaps ten, is the only one who can speak. The Cult took his sister. 'The shadow lady wants her for the big ceremony,' he says. 'She said when the moons align, the darkness will come.'\n\nYou learn more: The Cult holds their base in the old temple, three miles north. They have dozens of followers, and more arriving every day. And they're preparing for something called the Night of Convergence.\n\nThe boy begs to come with you. You should leave him\u2014he'll only slow you down. But his eyes remind you of someone. Princess Elara, perhaps. Another child you couldn't save.\n\n'Stay hidden,' you tell him. 'I'll bring your sister back.'\n\nThe promise feels like ash in your mouth. But it's the only thing you have left to give.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Take him with you\u2014he deserves justice",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_COMPANION",
        "effects": {
