  "THERON_CH1_SURVIVE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_SURVIVE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You fight like the knight you once were. The void runs through your veins, lending strength to your blade. Blood paints the rocks. Your wounds don't matter. Nothing matters but survival.\n\nFive Cultists fall. Then ten. The arrow in your shoulder tears as you move, but the pain is distant, irrelevant. You've entered the void-state\u2014pure combat, pure instinct.\n\nWhen it's over, you stand alone in the canyon, covered in blood. Yours or theirs\u2014you don't know. The void recedes, leaving exhaustion in its wake.\n\nYour injuries are serious. Without help, you won't survive the journey. But you've won. For now.\n\nA survivor among the Cultists\u2014a young woman, barely more than a girl\u2014lies dying against a rock. She looks at you with empty eyes.\n\n'The Convergence is coming,' she gasps. 'Nothing can stop it. Nothing.'\n\nShe dies. But her words echo in your mind.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Press on\u2014the mission continues",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_TEMPLE",
