  "THERON_CH1_ESCAPE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_ESCAPE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The void wraps around you like a cloak. Shadow and silence\u2014your old friends. You've forgotten how to use them, but they remember you.\n\nYou become darkness, slipping between the Cultists. Their blades pass through where you stood. Their arrows miss by inches. You flow like smoke, untouchable.\n\nSeconds later, you're at the temple entrance. The Cultists are still searching, confused.\n\nInside, the temple is vast\u2014a cathedral of shadows. The altar at its heart glows with sickly light. And there, suspended above it: children. Dozens of them. Sacrifices waiting to be made.\n\nThe void screams at you to act. But first, you need to understand. What is the Convergence? What does Vespera really want?\n\nYou find a hidden vantage point. And watch.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Attack now\u2014save the children",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_BATTLE",
        "effects": {
