  },
  "THERON_CH1_CAPTURE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH1_CAPTURE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You let them take you. It's not surrender\u2014it's strategy. They bind your hands with iron chains blessed by priests, but they don't know about the void inside you. It recognizes the chains for what they are: inconveniences.\n\nThey drag you to the temple. It's larger than you imagined\u2014a sprawling complex built over centuries, layer upon layer of worship and sacrifice. They don't just worship the void here. They study it.\n\nThe children are held in the lower chambers. Dozens of them, drugged into sleep. Their souls will feed the Convergence.\n\nBut you see something else: maps. Charts. The Cult's full plan.\n\nThe Night of Convergence is three days away. When the moons align, the seven shards will merge, tearing open a portal to the void itself. And through that portal, something ancient will emerge.\n\nThe Void Beast. A god that was sealed away at the Sundering. And now, it's waking up.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Break out\u2014stop the ritual",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_BATTLE",
        "effects": {
          "strength": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Play along\u2014await your chance",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_PRISON",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Use the void to contact Morgana",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_MESSAGE",
        "effects": {
          "void_magic": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "THERON_CH2_SHARD": {
    "id": "THERON_CH2_SHARD",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The research leads you to a crypt beneath the old cathedral. The seventh shard has been hidden here for thirty years\u2014a safeguard against the very convergence the Cult now pursues.\n\nThe chamber is sealed with void wards. Only someone who walks the darkness can enter. Only someone with nothing left to lose can claim the power.\n\nInside, the shard floats in a sphere of shadow. It's beautiful and terrible\u2014a piece of something that should never exist.\n\nWhen you touch it, visions flood your mind. The Void Beast, rising from its prison. The world ending in shadow. And at the center of it all: you, transformed into something beyond human.\n\nThe shard calls to you. It wants to be used. It wants you to become the Convergence's instrument\u2014or its weapon against the Cult.\n\nYou take the shard. Power floods through you\u2014darkness made manifest. And somewhere, across the kingdom, Vespera feels your presence.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Use the shard against the Cult",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_TEMPLE",
        "effects": {
          "void_magic": 3
        },
