        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_REPORT",
        "effects": {
          "charisma": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "THERON_CH2_CIRCLE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH2_CIRCLE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The Circle of Mages hides in plain sight\u2014a tower that appears different to each observer. You climb the stairs, each step taking you further from the world you knew.\n\nThe Archmage awaits at the top. An ageless woman with silver hair and eyes that see through time.\n\n'Theron Ashford,' she says. 'We wondered when you'd come.'\n\nShe knows about the Cult. About Vespera. About the Convergence.\n\n'The Void Beast was sealed at the Sundering,' she explains. 'Seven shards of its power were scattered across the kingdoms. The Cult has collected six. If they claim the seventh...'\n\nShe doesn't finish. She doesn't have to.\n\n'We can help you,' she offers. 'But the price is your service. Become our weapon against the darkness, and we'll help you destroy the Cult.'",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Accept their help\u2014you need power",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH2_TRAINING",
        "effects": {
