        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "THERON_CH2_TEMPLE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH2_TEMPLE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The Temple of Ash rises against the grey sky\u2014a monolith of black stone that's stood for a thousand years. This is where the first Convergence was attempted. This is where it will happen again.\n\nYou approach through the outer defenses. Cultists scatter before you\u2014either fleeing or attacking. You cut through them without mercy. The void has made you strong.\n\nInside, the temple is a maze. Chambers upon chambers, each dedicated to a different aspect of the void. Sacrifice rooms. Meditation halls. Torture chambers where the faithful are broken and remade.\n\nYou find the main chamber\u2014the heart of the temple. Seven pedestals ring a central dais. Six hold shards of terrible power, glowing with barely contained darkness. The seventh is empty.\n\nAt the dais stands a woman. Vespera. She turns, and you see her face.\n\nAnd you realize you know her.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Attack\u2014end this now",
        "leads_to": "THERON_CH3_BATTLE",
        "effects": {
          "combat": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Demand answers\u2014who is she?",
