  "THERON_CH2_VESPERA": {
    "id": "THERON_CH2_VESPERA",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "Vespera's face is beautiful and terrible. You know those features\u2014softened by decades, but unmistakable.\n\n'Princess Elara?'\n\nShe smiles. It's wrong. Too many teeth. Too much darkness.\n\n'Brother Theron. I wondered when you'd come. I've been waiting for you.'\n\nPrincess Elara\u2014the child you couldn't save\u2014is now the leader of the Cult. The fire didn't kill her. It transformed her.\n\n'I burned that night,' she says. 'I burned, and I died, and I was reborn in the void. The Beast spoke to me. It showed me the truth. The world is a wound, Theron. And the void will heal it.'\n\nShe reaches for you. 'Join me. Together, we can complete the Convergence. We can end all the pain. All the suffering. All the memories that keep you awake at night.'\n\nYour hand tightens on your sword. But she's not done.\n\n'Or kill me,' she says. 'But then the Convergence happens anyway. I'm not the key\u2014the shards are. And I have six of them.'",
