  "THERON_CH2_COMPANION": {
    "id": "THERON_CH2_COMPANION",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The boy, Caden, follows you through the hills. He doesn't speak much\u2014too much trauma\u2014but he moves quickly, staying close.\n\nYou make camp the first night under an overpass. He watches you sharpen your sword, then speaks.\n\n'My sister\u2014she has the void in her. She told me. She's scared, but she said it doesn't hurt anymore.'\n\nYou pause. The void in a child. That changes everything.\n\n'What was her name?'\n\n'Lily. She was taken three days ago. The shadow lady wanted her for something special.'\n\nThe boy looks at you with hope. 'You said you'd bring her back. Is that still true?'\n\nYou think about Princess Elara. About the fire. About all the things you've failed to save.\n\n'I'll try,' you say. And for the first time in years, you mean it.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
