  "THERON_CH2_TRAINING": {
    "id": "THERON_CH2_TRAINING",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The Circle of Mages offers training\u2014a way to master the void without being consumed. You accept, knowing it's probably a trap. But you need power.\n\nDays pass in isolation. The Archmage teaches you to feel the void\u2014and to control it. Not to deny your darkness, but to shape it.\n\nYou learn to draw shadows like weapons. To step through darkness like doors. To speak in the language of nothing.\n\nBut during your training, you discover a secret: The Circle isn't noble. They've been manipulating the kingdom for centuries. The king didn't die in a fire\u2014they killed him.\n\nAnd the queen? She's their puppet.\n\nEverything is a lie. The Cult. The Court. The Circle. Everyone serves the void in their own way.\n\nBut you also learn this: The seventh shard is hidden in the temple itself. The original seal, placed to prevent exactly this.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
