  "THERON_CH3_BATTLE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_BATTLE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You charge across the chamber, your blade aimed at Vespera's heart. She doesn't move\u2014doesn't even flinches.\n\nHer hand catches your sword. The blade stops an inch from her chest.\n\n'Such anger,' she whispers. 'Is it for me? Or for yourself?'\n\nShadows wrap around you. Not attacking\u2014embracing. The void recognizes its own.\n\n'You can't kill me, Theron. I'm part of you now. I've always been part of you\u2014the part you left in that burning palace.'\n\nShe releases you. You stagger back, weapon raised.\n\n'The Convergence will happen. One way or another. But you have a choice: be destroyed by it, or become its instrument.'\n\nAround you, the six shards begin to glow. The walls shake. The moors align.\n\nThe ritual is beginning.",
