  "THERON_CH3_TALK": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_TALK",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You lower your blade. Not surrender\u2014strategy.\n\n'Elara,' you say. 'Remember that night? The fire? You reached for me. I couldn't reach back.'\n\nHer eye twitches. The darkness wavers.\n\n'I've spent years running,' you continue. 'Trying to forget. Drinking to silence the voices. But they're not silenced. They just get louder.'\n\nYou step closer. 'Let me help you. We can end this together\u2014properly. No more sacrifices. No more children.'\n\nShe hesitates. For a moment, you see the girl she used to be\u2014sweet, innocent, full of light.\n\n'There's no proper way,' she whispers. 'The void is here. It's always been here. It's in our blood\u2014our family line.'\n\nYour blood. The Ashford line. You've carried the void since birth.\n\n'Then we carry it together,' you say. 'But choose for yourself. Choose to end it.'",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Help her destroy the shards\u2014end the line",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_REDEEMED",
        "effects": {
          "honor": 4
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Become her partner\u2014guide her darkness",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_COMMANDER",
        "effects": {
          "charisma": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
