  "THERON_CH3_JOIN": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_JOIN",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You kneel. The void rises to greet you\u2014a wave of darkness that feels like coming home.\n\nElara touches your head, her fingers cold as ice.\n\n'Welcome home, brother. We've been waiting for you.'\n\nThe power floods through you\u2014seven shards merged into one. You feel the seal breaking. The Beast stirring.\n\nAnd you understand what you've become: the Vessel. The new prison for the Void Beast. The door that's about to open.\n\n'Is this what you wanted?' you ask.\n\n'No,' she says. 'This is what we needed. The old gods must have a host. And you're stronger than any cultist.'\n\nThe convergence begins. Not with fire and destruction\u2014but with silence. The void consumes everything. Your mind. Your memories. Your soul.\n\nBut in the end, you control it. You become its master.\n\nAnd that's when you realize: you were never the hero. You were always the monster. You just didn't know it yet.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Embrace the darkness\u2014become the Undying",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_COMMANDER",
        "effects": {
