  "THERON_CH3_RITUAL": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_RITUAL",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You watch from the shadows as Vespera begins the ritual.\n\nThe six shards rise from their pedestals, circling the dais. She stands at the center, her arms raised, her voice chanting in a language older than words.\n\nThe children wake\u2014dozens of them. Their eyes glow with void light. They're not victims\u2014they're components. Fuel for the machine.\n\nThe portal opens slowly\u2014a tear in reality itself. Beyond it, you see the Beast. A darkness beyond darkness. A hunger beyond hunger.\n\nIt looks at you.\n\nIt sees you.\n\n'Join us,' it whispers. 'You've always been ours.'\n\nYou could run. Let it consume the world. But then you remember Princess Elara\u2014the child she used to be. The sister you couldn't save.\n\nNo more.",
