  "THERON_CH3_SEAL": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_SEAL",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The seal is ancient\u2014a binding placed during the Sundering to contain the Void Beast forever. It sits at the heart of the temple, waiting.\n\nYou touch the stone. Visions flood your mind.\n\nThe Sundering. The original convergence. Countless deaths to seal away a god. And the knights who made that sacrifice\u2014your ancestors.\n\nYou've been running from this your whole life. It was always your destiny.\n\nThe void inside you responds to the seal. It wants in. It wants rest.\n\nYou step into the chamber, and the seal closes around you. The darkness floods into you\u2014concentrated, overwhelming. Your body becomes the prison. Your soul becomes the lock.\n\nYou scream\u2014but the scream becomes silence. The void becomes you.\n\nAnd in that eternal moment, you feel peace. The first peace you've known since the fire.\n\nThey'll never escape. Neither will you.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Accept the seal\u2014you are the prison now",
