      }
    ]
  },
  "THERON_CH3_CONFRONTATION": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_CONFRONTATION",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The seventh shard burns in your hand. You've drawn upon power that should never exist\u2014and you've made your choice.\n\nVespera sees you across the chamber. Her eyes widen.\n\n'You got the seventh,' she breathes. 'How?'\n\n'I am the seventh,' you say. 'I've always been. Since the fire. Since Elara died. Since I became darkness itself.'\n\nThe shard responds to your will. You could destroy the Cult. All of them. The entire temple. Everything.\n\nBut that would make you the monster they've been fighting.\n\nInstead, you focus the power into the seal\u2014the ancient binding that held the Beast once. It won't hold forever, but it will hold.\n\n'No,' Vespera screams. 'Don't\u2014'\n\nThe seal activates. The shards shatter. The portal collapses.\n\nAnd you're left standing in the ruins, holding nothing.\n\nThe Beast is sealed. The Cult is scattered. And you?\n\nYou're empty.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Accept your fate\u2014no regrets",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_REDEEMED",
        "effects": {
          "honor": 4
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Walk away\u2014find peace somewhere",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_HOLLOW",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Find new purpose\u2014the knight continues",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_COMMANDER",
        "effects": {
          "charisma": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "THERON_CH3_EXPOSE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_EXPOSE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "The truth is a weapon. And you've just loaded the cannon.\n\nYou return to Crownhaven with proof: documents, witnesses, the testimony of a dozen survivors. The Circle's conspiracy. The Cult's infiltration. Morgana's true allegiance.\n\nBut things have changed while you were gone. Queen Seraphina is dead. Assassinated. And in her place sits a new ruler\u2014someone you've never seen.\n\nThe court is divided. The kingdom is on the brink of civil war.\n\n'Vespera demanded this,' Morgana says. 'The Cult wanted chaos. They needed the queen dead to begin the Convergence.'\n\nBut it's too late. The shards are aligning. The portal is opening.\n\nYou have one choice left: Use what you've learned to stop the Convergence, or use it to claim power.\n\nThe throne sits empty. And you have the strength to take it.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Claim the throne\u2014restore order",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_COMMANDER",
        "effects": {
          "charisma": 4
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Expose everyone\u2014let the kingdom decide",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_REDEEMED",
        "effects": {
          "honor": 3
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Walk away\u2014let it burn",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_HOLLOW",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": -2
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "THERON_CH3_ALONE": {
    "id": "THERON_CH3_ALONE",
    "character": "THERON",
    "description": "You leave both sides to destroy each other. The Circle. The Cult. The Court. Let them tear each other apart.\n\nBut the world doesn't end. Hours pass, then days. The portal doesn't open. The Beast doesn't rise.\n\nSomething has changed. Vespera is dead\u2014killed by her own followers. The shards have scattered. The Convergence has failed.\n\nYou wander the kingdom, aimless. The void inside you has quieted\u2014or perhaps it's just sleeping.\n\nYou find yourself at the broken tavern where this all began. The mug is still there, waiting.\n\nYoupour it out.\n\nFor the first time in years, you don't reach for the drink. There's no peace in it. No forgetting. Only more dreams of flames.\n\nBut perhaps there's something else. Perhaps there's the beginning of a different path.\n\nYou leave the tavern. The road stretches ahead. And for the first time in years, you don't know where it leads.\n\nThat's okay. You'll figure it out as you go.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Move forward\u2014a new beginning",
        "leads_to": "THERON_ENDING_REDEEMED",
