  "VEX_CH1_AMBUSH": {
    "id": "VEX_CH1_AMBUSH",
    "character": "VEX",
    "description": "You trail the smugglers through winding tunnels, staying just out of sight. They lead you to a small cavern lit by torches\u2014a waystation. Two guards stand watch while the others disappear into a side chamber.\n\nYou could slip past them, but they'd spot you eventually. Instead, you wait. When one guard walks alone toward a privy, you strike. A quick garrote, a silent end. The second guard never sees you coming. Your blade finds his throat before he can cry out.\n\nIn the side chamber, you find their leader\u2014Corvus, a mid-level Guild lieutenant. He's terrified when he sees you, the thief who stole the Obsidian Ledger. \n\n\"Please,\" he whimpers. \"I have information. The Guild knows you're heading to Dustwall. They're waiting. But there's more\u2014I know where the Shadowmaster hides. Kill me or let me go, either way, you're walking into a trap.\"",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Kill Corvus and take his information",
        "leads_to": "VEX_CH1_SISTER",
        "effects": {
