  "VEX_CH2_CONFRONT": {
    "id": "VEX_CH2_CONFRONT",
    "character": "VEX",
    "description": "The Guild finds you before you can reach Miravel. A dozen enforcers surround the alley, their blades drawn. At their head stands Vance, the Guild's Hunter\u2014their finest killer. His smile is cold as he regards you.\n\n\"Vex Shadowstep,\" he says. \"You've caused quite a lot of trouble.\"\n\n\"I've caused exactly enough.\" You keep your hand near your dagger, watching for an opening.\n\n\"Give us the ledger, and the Shadowmaster will consider mercy. Fight, and we'll take it from your corpse. Either way, you're not leaving this alley.\"\n\nThe tension is palpable. You could try to fight your way out\u2014difficult with twelve armed opponents. You could negotiate\u2014maybe buy time. Or you could surrender and look for an opportunity to escape later.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Fight your way out",
        "leads_to": "VEX_CH2_FIGHT",
        "effects": {
