    "type": "story"
  },
  "VEX_CH2_SURRENDER": {
    "id": "VEX_CH2_SURRENDER",
    "character": "VEX",
    "description": "You drop your weapons, hands raised. \"I yield.\"\n\nThe enforcers hesitate\u2014they expected a fight. Vance approaches cautiously, binding your wrists with cord. \"Smart. The master will decide your fate.\"\n\nThey drag you through the city's underbelly to the Guild's stronghold. You're thrown into a cell, but it's comfortable\u2014a message that the Shadowmaster wants you alive. Days pass. You're fed, given water. Then, finally, they come for you.\n\nThe Shadowmaster waits in his throne room. He's older than you expected, silver-haired but still dangerous. His eyes study you like you're an interesting puzzle.\n\n\"You stole my ledger,\" he says. \"But you didn't sell it. Why?\"\n\n\"Because the Guild needs to burn.\"\n\nHe laughs\u2014a dry, hollow sound. \"Or perhaps... you simply want to lead it instead.\"",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Play along and infiltrate the Guild",
        "leads_to": "VEX_CH3_TREASON",
        "effects": {
