  "VEX_CH3_COLLECTOR": {
    "id": "VEX_CH3_COLLECTOR",
    "character": "VEX",
    "description": "Miravel's shop is hidden behind a bookbinder's storefront in the Merchant Quarter. The old woman who runs it leads you through a maze of corridors into a vaulted chamber where treasures from a hundred criminal enterprises gleam in lamplight.\n\nMiravel herself is younger than you expected\u2014perhaps thirty, with dark hair and sharper eyes than a hawk. She doesn't look up from the ledger she's examining when you enter.\n\n\"Vex Shadowstep. I wondered when you'd come.\"\n\n\"You know me?\"\n\n\"I know everyone.\" She finally meets your gaze. \"This ledger\u2014it's genuine. The names, the accounts, the secrets. With this, I could bring the Guild to its knees. Or I could sell it back to them for triple.\"\n\n\"You're not going to do either.\"\n\nHer smile is thin. \"No? Then tell me\u2014what's your offer?\"",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Make a deal with Miravel",
        "leads_to": "VEX_CH3_TREASON",
        "effects": {
