  "VEX_CH3_TREASON": {
    "id": "VEX_CH3_TREASON",
    "character": "VEX",
    "description": "The plan comes together in whispers. You've made deals with everyone\u2014the Guild, Miravel, even Corvus the double agent. But you have your own plans, your own agenda. The ledger is the weapon, and everyone is pointing it at everyone else.\n\nIn the Guild headquarters, you meet with the Shadowmaster one final time. He believes you've come to swear loyalty. In a way, you have.\n\n\"I've decided,\" you tell him. \"The Guild is the future. I'm here to join it\u2014properly this time.\"\n\nHe smiles and extends his hand. \"Welcome home, Vex Shadowstep.\"\n\nYou take his hand\u2014and drive a poisoned dagger into his chest.\n\nThe chaos begins. Miravel's forces attack from outside. Corvus reveals himself to the Guild. And you stand in the middle, the ledger in one hand and the Shadowmaster's dying breath in the other. Every alliance broken. Every enemy fighting each other.\n\nNow it's time to finish this.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Seize power as the new Shadowmaster",
        "leads_to": "VEX_ENDING_SHADOWKING",
        "effects": {
