  "VEX_CH4_TEMPLE": {
    "id": "VEX_CH4_TEMPLE",
    "character": "VEX",
    "description": "The Guild's true headquarters lies beneath the Temple of Shadows\u2014an ancient complex built long before the city rose above it. You've fought your way through layers of defenses, through assassins and traps and loyalists who would die for the Guild.\n\nNow you stand in the central chamber. The Shadowmaster waits on his throne, flanked by his personal guard. But he raises a hand, and they stand down.\n\n\"Vex,\" he says, almost warmly. \"You've come further than anyone expected. But this ends here.\"\n\n\"It ends when the Guild is gone.\"\n\n\"The Guild is eternal. We are the shadows that move beneath the light. You cannot destroy us\u2014you can only join us.\"\n\nHis blade materializes in his hand, a curved thing that drinks the torchlight. \"But I'll give you a choice. Face me in single combat. Win, and you walk free. Lose, and your soul joins the shadows forever.\"\n\nThe challenge hangs in the air.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Accept the duel",
        "leads_to": "VEX_CH4_DUEL",
        "effects": {
