        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH1_GATHER": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH1_GATHER",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You spend three months in the dark corners of Crownhaven, listening.\n\nThe Vance Trading Company's books are a labyrinth of falsified ledgers. Your father's 'accident' wasn't the first death Castellan arranged\u2014and it won't be the last. You find records of merchants who 'retired' early, of partners who 'moved away,' of competitors whose ships 'disappeared.'\n\nBut you find something else. Your father's last deal before he died: a shipment from the eastern territories, contents classified. He sent it to the family vault before... before.\n\nThe vault is in Castellan's estate now. Guarded. Warded. But not impenetrable.\n\nYou also find chatter about the Ashfield Cult. They meet in old temples. They worship something called the Hollow. And Castellan attends their ceremonies.\n\nYour parents weren't killed for the company. They were killed for what they found.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Investigate the Cult connection",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH1_CULT",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Study the vault's defenses",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH1_VAULT",
        "effects": {
          "stealth": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Contact your father's old contacts",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH1_CONTACTS",
        "effects": {
