        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH1_CONTACTS": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH1_CONTACTS",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "Your father's old network is smaller than you remember\u2014but more loyal.\n\nMarco, his old bookkeeper, weeps when he sees you. 'I knew you'd come back,' he whispers. 'Your father was the only good noble I ever met. The company was his heart.'\n\nHe's kept records\u2014real records\u2014of every transaction Castellan made. Every bribe, every forgery, every death. Your father was building a case against the Cult. He was gathering evidence.\n\n'He found something in the eastern shipment,' Marco says. 'A piece of an old crown. He wanted to destroy it. That's when they came for him.'\n\nHe gives you a key to the old family vault\u2014and the name of a contact in the Circle of Mages. 'They can help you. If you let them.'\n\nYou have resources now. Information. A path forward.\n\nThe game begins.",
