  "ELARA_CH1_ALLIES": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH1_ALLIES",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You can't destroy a noble alone. You need an army of whispers.\n\nThe lower city is full of people with grudges\u2014the dockworkers Castellan cheated, the merchants he ruined, the nobles he embarrassed. You gather them slowly, carefully. A reputation takes time, but it spreads.\n\nYour network grows: thieves who owe you favors, servants who hear things, guards who remember loyalty. You become the whisper in the shadows, the name people speak in dark corners.\n\nBy the third month, you have twelve reliable contacts. By the sixth, twenty-three. And somewhere in between, you realize: you're not just seeking revenge anymore. You're building something.\n\nA network becomes an organization. An organization becomes power. And power, in the right hands, becomes justice.\n\nCastellan doesn't know what's coming. But you do.",
