  "ELARA_CH2_NETWORK": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH2_NETWORK",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "The Circle of Mages hides in plain sight\u2014a tower that appears different to each observer.\n\nYou climb the stairs, each step taking you further from the world you knew. The Archmage is ancient, her eyes holding centuries of knowledge.\n\n'We know why you're here,' she says. 'The crown piece. Castellan stole it from your parents.'\n\nShe explains: The crown is Aethon's crown\u2014seven pieces, each containing a fragment of the first silence. United, they could unmake reality itself. The Cult wants that power. Your parents tried to destroy the piece they found. They died for it.\n\n'We can help you,' she offers. 'But the price is your service. Help us destroy the Cult, and we'll help you destroy Castellan.'\n\nYou have allies now. The question is: what are you willing to become?",
