  "ELARA_CH2_CIRCLE": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH2_CIRCLE",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "The Circle trains you in ways you never imagined. Magic\u2014or what passes for it in your blood. The void responds to your touch, dark and hungry.\n\n'The Vance family carries old blood,' the Archmage says. 'Your ancestor served Aethon. That's why the crown called to your parents. That's why it calls to you.'\n\nYou learn to pull shadows from the corners, to move without sound, to kill without\u75d5\u8ff9. Your combat grows sharper. Your mind grows darker.\n\nIn three months, you're ready. The Circle has gathered intelligence: Castellan plans to sell the crown piece to the Cult's leader, Vespera. The transaction happens in one week.\n\nYou have one chance. Fail, and the Cult gets what they want. Succeed, and you get your answers.\n\nEverything builds to this.",
    "choices": [
