  "ELARA_CH2_ATTACK": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH2_ATTACK",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You don't wait. Five years of patience burns in a single heartbeat.\n\nYour blade finds the gap in his armor before his guards can react\u2014straight through the heart. Lord Castellan gasps, more surprised than afraid.\n\n'You're...' he rasps. 'The Vance girl.'\n\n'The one you murdered,' you whisper. 'Say hello to my parents for me.'\n\nHe slumps. The guards finally react, but you're already through the window, vanishing into the night. The estate will be in chaos for hours.\n\nBut something is wrong. It was too easy. And in his study, you find something that changes everything: a letter from the Cult. Your parents didn't just find the crown piece\u2014they tried to destroy it. The piece called to them, and they tried to unmake what was unmade.\n\nThat's why they died.\n\nYou have your revenge. But the question remains: what now?",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Search the vault\u2014the crown calls",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH3_VAULT",
        "effects": {
          "stealth": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Flee the city\u2014it's over",
