        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH2_INFILTRATE": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH2_INFILTRATE",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You join the Cult as an initiate. It takes three months of pretending to believe, of chanting words you don't understand, of watching ceremonies that make your stomach turn.\n\nBut you learn. You learn about their hierarchy, their plans, their leader. Vespera\u2014the shadow lady\u2014is more than a cult leader. She's something else. Something that burned and was reborn in the fires of the old temple.\n\nYou also learn about the crown. Six pieces gathered. One piece still missing\u2014 Castellan's piece.\n\nThey plan a ceremony: the Night of Convergence, when all seven pieces will unite. They call it the birth of a new world. You call it the end of everything.\n\nCastellan is supposed to deliver the piece tonight. And you're the only one who can stop it.\n\nThe question is: how far are you willing to go?",
