  "ELARA_CH2_CONFRONT": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH2_CONFRONT",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You march into Castellan's study like you own the kingdom. Because soon, you will.\n\nHe looks up from his books, and recognition flickers in his eyes. 'You. The Vance girl.'\n\n'Me,' you say. 'Five years ago, you murdered my parents. You took everything. Now I'm here to take it back.'\n\nHis hand moves for the bell\u2014but Marco's guards are already at the door. Your network. Your people.\n\n'Wait,' Castellan says. 'I can explain.'\n\nAnd he does. Your parents found the crown piece. They were going to destroy it. But the Cult made him do it\u2014made him complicit. 'They would have killed me,' he says. 'They would have killed everyone I loved.'\n\nHe offers you a deal: the crown piece, yours to do with as you will. In exchange, you let him live.\n\nDo you take the deal?",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Take the deal\u2014he's useless anyway",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH3_VAULT",
        "effects": {
