        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH2_REVEAL": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH2_REVEAL",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You step into the light. No more masks. No more pretending.\n\nCastellan's face goes white. 'You're\u2014' But he doesn't finish.\n\n'Five years,' you say. 'I've watched. I've waited. I've built a network that could destroy you in a single night. But I'm not here to destroy you.'\n\nYou pull out your father's letter\u2014the one he never got to send. 'I'm here to ask: why?'\n\nHis voice breaks. 'The Cult... they made me. My family, my children\u2014they threatened them. Your parents found the crown piece and wanted to destroy it. I couldn't let them\u2014the Cult would have killed everyone I love.'\n\n'But you killed them,' you say. 'My parents. In cold blood.'\n\n'I didn't,' he whispers. 'I tried to stop them. I failed.'\n\nThe truth hurts worse than the lie. He wasn't the mastermind\u2014he was just a coward. And cowards are the most dangerous people in the world.\n\nNow you have your choice.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Forgive him\u2014he's just a pawn",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH3_VAULT",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Kill him\u2014no excuses",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH2_ATTACK",
        "effects": {
          "strength": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Turn him in\u2014the law decides",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH2_SURRENDER",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH3_VAULT": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH3_VAULT",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "The Vance family vault is exactly where you remember. The heavy iron door, the wards your father placed, the darkness that seems to breathe.\n\nInside, the crown piece waits on a pedestal. It's smaller than you imagined\u2014a ring of black metal that seems to absorb light. When you touch it, the world goes silent.\n\nVisions flood your mind: Aethon the Undying, screaming as something beyond comprehension tears at his soul. The Void Beast. A god that eats gods. Aethon shattered his crown to keep it from falling into the Beast's hands. Seven pieces, scattered across time.\n\nYour parents understood. That's why they tried to destroy it. The piece in your hand could reunite the crown\u2014and free something terrible.\n\nBut it could also give you power. Power to destroy the Cult. Power to protect everything your parents loved.\n\nPower always has a price.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Take it\u2014use its power",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH3_TAKE",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Destroy it\u2014end the threat",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH3_DESTROY",
        "effects": {
          "charisma": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Give it to the Circle",
