        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH3_TAKE": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH3_TAKE",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You take the crown piece. And everything changes.\n\nThe power floods through you\u2014shadows, darkness, void. Your parents' memories become your memories. Their training becomes your training. Their enemies become your enemies.\n\nYou see the Cult's plans. The Night of Convergence. The sacrifices. The portal to the Void Beast. You see everything, spread before you like a map.\n\nYou feel unstoppable. You feel immortal. You feel... hungry.\n\nThe piece whispers to you, promising more. Six other pieces exist. Together, you could rule the world. Unmake your enemies. Create a new reality where everything is just, where nothing hurts.\n\nThe path to the Cult lies open. The path to Vespera lies open. The question is: what will you become?",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Find the other pieces\u2014become power",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_CONFRONTATION",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Destroy the Cult now",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_CONFRONTATION",
        "effects": {
          "combat": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Use it to destroy Castellan",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_REVENGE",
        "effects": {
          "strength": 2
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH3_DESTROY": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH3_DESTROY",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You destroy the crown piece. It takes everything\u2014your parents' legacy, your birthright, your power. But it's done.\n\nThe piece shatters like glass, releasing something older than light. Your parents' spirits, perhaps. Or just the emptiness they tried to protect.\n\nWithout the piece, the Cult's plan fails. The Night of Convergence becomes just another failed ritual. Vespera screams in the distance\u2014you feel it.\n\nCastellan falls to the Circle's justice. The evidence you've gathered cleans up the rest of his network. The kingdom breathes easier.\n\nBut you're empty. The power you could have had, the answers you might have found\u2014all gone.\n\nYou have your vengeance. But you also have a choice: what now? Without the piece, you have no destiny. You have only the life you build.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Join the Circle\u2014find new purpose",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_EXPOSE",
        "effects": {
          "intelligence": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Walk away\u2014it's over",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_AFTERMATH",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Continue hunting the Cult",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_EXPOSE",
        "effects": {
          "combat": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH3_CIRCLE": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH3_CIRCLE",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You give the piece to the Circle. They promise to destroy it properly, to seal it away where no one can ever find it.\n\nThe Archmage looks at you with something like respect. 'Your parents would be proud,' she says. 'They tried to do this. You succeeded.'\n\nBut you feel the loss. The piece called to you\u2014your family's legacy, your birthright. Without it, you're just another survivor.\n\nThe Circle offers you a place. Not as a mage\u2014they see your potential, but it's too late\u2014but as a hunter. The Cult remains, scattered but not destroyed. Vespera remains, wounded but not beaten.\n\nThey want you to finish the job. And you want the same thing.\n\nThe war isn't over. It's just changing form.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Accept\u2014the hunt continues",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_EXPOSE",
        "effects": {
          "combat": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "B",
        "text": "Refuse\u2014you've done enough",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_AFTERMATH",
        "effects": {
          "humanity": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      },
      {
        "letter": "C",
        "text": "Hunt Vespera yourself",
        "leads_to": "ELARA_CH4_REVENGE",
        "effects": {
          "strength": 1
        },
        "requires": null
      }
    ]
  },
  "ELARA_CH3_CULT": {
    "id": "ELARA_CH3_CULT",
    "character": "ELARA",
    "description": "You find the Cult's temple\u2014a burned-out ruin where they practice their rituals.\n\nThey're preparing for something: the Night of Convergence, when all seven pieces of the crown will unite. They have six already. Without Castellan's piece, they're missing one\u2014but they have plans to get it.\n\nThe leader, Vespera, is something else. She was a princess, once\u2014a saint of the old Light. The fire changed her. The void remade her. She's beautiful and terrible, and she's waiting for you.\n\n'I knew you'd come,' she says. 'The Vance blood calls to the crown. And you're the last of it.'\n\nShe offers you a choice: join her, and help complete the Convergence. Or die here, like your parents.\n\nThe choice is easy.",
    "choices": [
      {
        "letter": "A",
        "text": "Fight her\u2014end this now",
